---
layout: base.njk
title: "Amenities | Mona Shores Flats"
description: "In-unit washer/dryer, granite kitchens, fitness center, pickleball courts, dog run, playground, clubhouse and detached garages in Norton Shores, MI."
---

<section class="section" style="padding-top:clamp(110px,14vw,180px)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="stack" data-reveal>
      <div class="eyebrow">What's Included</div>
      <h2>Everything you'd expect — on day one.</h2>
      <p class="lead">A brand-new 2025 community with the finishes and shared spaces that make daily life easy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid amenities" style="margin-top:clamp(36px,5vw,56px)">
      {% for a in site.amenities %}
      <div class="amenity" data-reveal><div class="amenity__ico">{{ a.icon }}</div><div class="amenity__name">{{ a.name }}</div></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split" data-reveal>
      <div class="split__media"><img src="/img/kitchen.jpg" alt="Granite kitchen with stainless appliances"></div>
      <div class="stack">
        <div class="eyebrow">Inside every home</div>
        <h2>Granite, stainless, and space to spread out.</h2>
        <div class="points" style="margin-top:18px">
          <div class="point"><h3>Chef-ready kitchens</h3><p>Granite countertops with island layouts, full stainless-steel appliance packages, and a dishwasher.</p></div>
          <div class="point"><h3>In-unit laundry</h3><p>Full-size washer and dryer in every home — no shared machines, no laundromat.</p></div>
          <div class="point"><h3>Light & air</h3><p>High ceilings, open-concept living, large windows, central A/C, and a private balcony or patio.</p></div>
          <div class="point"><h3>Room for everything</h3><p>Generous closets, extra storage, and detached garages available to rent.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section cta">
  <div class="wrap stack center">
    <h2>Come tour the community.</h2>
    <p>{{ site.special }}</p>
    <div class="cta__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="/contact/#tour">Schedule a Tour</a>
      <a class="btn btn--accent btn--lg" href="{{ site.urls.availability }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Check Availability →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
